thread.title: Shuting Liu
thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Shuting Liu

author: Shuting Liu
title: Shuting Liu
text: I moved from Sydney to Melbourne recently and used the mobile storage service with TAXIBOX. It proves to be a money valued choice. The whole process went smoothly and all the staff I have contact with were nice, approachable and helpful. Thanks guys! Will definitely recommend this company to any friend who will have an interstate moving.
